    <summary><span data-ttu-id="c1b44-101">指定是否缓存图块画笔对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c1b44-101">Specifies whether to cache tiled brush objects.</span></span></summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c1b44-102">默认情况下，[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] 不缓存 <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingBrush> 和 <xref:System.Windows.Media.VisualBrush> 对象的呈现内容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c1b44-102">By default, [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] does not cache the rendered contents of <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingBrush> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.VisualBrush> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c1b44-103">在静态方案中，无论场景中的画笔如何变化，而不是使用缓存来提供好处，因为它可节省视频内存。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c1b44-103">In static scenarios where neither the contents nor the use of the brush in the scene is changing, not caching provides a benefit because it conserves video memory.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c1b44-104">当使用静态内容的画笔以非静态方式使用时，[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] 的默认行为是每隔一帧重新呈现画笔的全部内容，即使内容不变也是如此。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c1b44-104">When a brush with static content is used in a non-static way, the default behavior of [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] is to re-render the entire content of the brush every frame, even though the content is unchanging.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c1b44-105">例如，当静态 <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingBrush> 或 <xref:System.Windows.Media.VisualBrush> 映射到旋转三维对象的图面时，将发生这种情况。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c1b44-105">For example, this will happen when a static <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingBrush> or <xref:System.Windows.Media.VisualBrush> is mapped to the surface of a rotating 3D object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c1b44-106">重新呈现静态内容可能会对性能产生负面影响。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c1b44-106">Re-rendering the static content can have a negative impact on performance.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c1b44-107">通过将画笔的 "<xref:System.Windows.Media.RenderOptions.CachingHint%2A> 附加" 属性设置为 "缓存"，可以使用平铺画笔对象的缓存版本来提高性能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c1b44-107">By setting the <xref:System.Windows.Media.RenderOptions.CachingHint%2A> attached property on the brush to Cache, you can increase performance by using cached versions of the tiled brush objects.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c1b44-108"><xref:System.Windows.Media.RenderOptions.CacheInvalidationThresholdMinimum%2A> 和 <xref:System.Windows.Media.RenderOptions.CacheInvalidationThresholdMaximum%2A> 属性值是相对大小的值，这些值决定了 <xref:System.Windows.Media.TileBrush> 对象因刻度的变化而应重新生成的时间。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c1b44-108">The <xref:System.Windows.Media.RenderOptions.CacheInvalidationThresholdMinimum%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.RenderOptions.CacheInvalidationThresholdMaximum%2A> property values are relative size values that determine when the <xref:System.Windows.Media.TileBrush> object should be regenerated due to changes in scale.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c1b44-109">例如，通过将 <xref:System.Windows.Media.RenderOptions.CacheInvalidationThresholdMaximum%2A> 属性设置为2.0，只需在其大小超过当前缓存大小的两倍时重新生成 <xref:System.Windows.Media.TileBrush> 的缓存。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c1b44-109">For example, by setting the <xref:System.Windows.Media.RenderOptions.CacheInvalidationThresholdMaximum%2A> property to 2.0, the cache for the <xref:System.Windows.Media.TileBrush> only needs to be regenerated when its size exceeds twice the size of the current cache.</span></span>  
  
   
  
